        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "PII in Agentic Pipelines"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Personally identifiable information (PII) \u2014 names, email addresses, phone numbers, social security numbers, dates of birth, IP addresses, and similar data \u2014 presents a specific challenge in agentic systems because the agent may encounter PII in multiple contexts simultaneously: a user message, a retrieved database record, a tool result, and a sub-agent response. Each source needs the same protection, but the data may arrive in different formats, with different confidences, and at different points in the pipeline."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The goal is to ensure that PII is "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "detected with sufficient accuracy",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "protected using the right mechanism",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " for its risk level, and "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "never passed to components that do not need it",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "bold"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " \u2014 including the LLM itself, where it becomes part of a potentially logged, cached, and fine-tuning-eligible context window."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "PII Protection Pipeline"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "attrs": {
          "src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,",
          "alt": "PII Protection Pipeline \u2014 detect, classify, protect, enforce",
